RIGHT VPN Privacy Policy

At RIGHT VPN, we take your privacy seriously and are committed to protecting your personal information. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our VPN services.

Information We Collect:
- Personal information: When you sign up for RIGHT VPN, we may collect your name, email address, and payment details to process your account and billing.
- Connection data: We collect information about your device, operating system, IP address, session duration, and bandwidth usage to optimize our service and ensure proper functioning.

How We Use Your Information:
- To provide and maintain our VPN services.
- To improve our services, develop new features, and enhance your user experience.
- To protect against fraudulent activities and maintain the security of our network and users.
- To communicate with you regarding updates, new features, and important announcements.

Information Sharing:
- We do not sell, lease, or rent your personal information to any third parties.
- We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our business or service you as long as they agree to keep it confidential.
- We may disclose your information if required by law or to protect our rights, safety, or the safety of others.

Data Retention:
- We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this privacy policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.

Information Security:
- We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information and maintain data security.
- However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

Your Choices and Rights:
- You may review, update, or delete your personal information by contacting us.
- You may also opt-out of receiving promotional communications from us.

Changes to this Privacy Policy:
- We reserve the right to update or modify this privacy policy at any time, and any changes will be effective upon posting.
